        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisites</strong> trained in Athletics</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You are wielding only a single one-handed melee weapon and have your other hand or hands free.</p>\n<hr>\n<p>You adopt a fencing stance that improves your control over your weapon. While you are in this stance, you gain a +1 circumstance bonus to Athletics checks to Disarm and a +2 circumstance bonus to your Reflex DC when defending against checks to Disarm you. In addition, you can attempt to Disarm creatures up to two sizes larger than you.</p>",
